value:
Where are you, Ban-Ban? I'm...
so frightened...
Are you...another part of my dream?

If I keep my eyes closed like this...
time will just pass me by...

Th-this is...something I must give you.
It's from $Nf...

You shouldn't come so close to me...
Bad things happen.
No! I-I can't... I'm so scared!

I am...Tiki... The holy grounds must
be cleansed of those who taint it...

I'm s-so...scared... Don't leave me...
Please...$k$p...Hm? O-oh, $Nu!$k$pIn my dreams...I always have the
same nightmare... Everyone leaves...
and I stay behind...$k$pBut you're different... You stay with
me, $Nu...$k$pPlease, promise you'll never leave
me... I hate being alone...
I am... Who... Who am I? ...Tiki?
Grr-agh, ah! N-no... Stay away from me!
Don't...come any closer... If you do, I... I don't want to hurt you!
There's...a voice in my head... It's telling me to...remember.
I will burn...everything. With all my strength!
Ban-Ban... Everyone... Where did you all go?
I had a...a terrible dream... Will you sit with me? Please?
